{"tid":1499322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵禁制令，無人講？","createTime":"2019-08-23T16:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T01:12:12.000Z","uid":182519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"28d973bba521205a5b8b418a04086e49acebad59","tid":1499322,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:19:11.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】港鐵代表今晚約9時到高等法院入稟緊急申請臨時禁制令，由高院法官周家明處理申請。聆訊禁止公衆傳媒旁聽，內庭處理申請。港鐵由余若海資深大律師代表，約晚上9時半到庭。聆訊歷時10分鐘，法官批出禁制令，生效期至下周五。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵今午發表新聞稿指示威者近日以粗言穢語辱罵港鐵人員，更破壞入閘機，塗污車站內外，令車站入口未能如常開放。港鐵表明保留權利作出追究，更會向法庭尋求包括禁制令等適當的法律措施作緩解，以確保港鐵網絡的安全及正常運作。<br />\n<br />\n記者 劉曉曦 蕭文軒"},{"pid":"3661c37df002e44b8a0ea3859c4786663f043ed6","tid":1499322,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:27:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"556ef4cf342fea2d1099c3dfb9d35367c12b5ccd","tid":1499322,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:28:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19ab0049a4fa549cf5200f4cdaf93ffc1292eac7","tid":1499322,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:28:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf43a54f49b55579c74d08f583d7e831302a8ed0","tid":1499322,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc71e58c8648762a15a19ad08a9d49493ed0169","tid":1499322,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:29:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63442e3b6749b4e4c2b328db6ae454ddb596eedc","tid":1499322,"uid":48315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢<br />\n有禁制令你就唔去唔圍架啦咩    <br />\n有本事咪撚比人入 <br />\n我嘟左百達通就係客 你理得我行去邊"},{"pid":"08ea5c66666a47bbe983cc6d7e3a80412814bd0d","tid":1499322,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:30:12.000Z","